remarks.format:
## Remarks

`SKPathBuilder` provides a mutable builder for constructing paths. Use <xref:SkiaSharp.SKPathBuilder.Snapshot> to get a read-only copy of the path so far, or <xref:SkiaSharp.SKPathBuilder.Detach> to take ownership and reset the builder. Always dispose the builder when done.

## Examples

```csharp
using var builder = new SKPathBuilder();
builder.MoveTo(0, 0);
builder.LineTo(100, 0);
builder.LineTo(50, 100);
builder.Close();
using var path = builder.Detach();
canvas.DrawPath(path, paint);
```
